<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <title>Rujin Shrestha</title>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
</head>

<body>
    <!-- <%- include('partials/inprogress') %> -->
    <header>
        <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
    </header>

    <main>
        <div id="to-top">
            <a href="#">
                <i class="fas fa-angle-up"></i>
            </a>
        </div>
        <section id="home">
            <p>Hi!</p>
            <p>I am <span class="green">Rujin Shrestha.</span></p>
            <button>Download Resume</button>
            <div id="scroll-down">
                <a href="#about">
                    Scroll down
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                </a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- ABOUT ME SECTION  -->

        <section id="about">
            <div class="content two-columns">
                <div class="content-text">
                    <p>I come from <span class="green">Kathmandu, Nepal</span> and I am currently a final year Computer
                        Science
                        student at <span class="green">Vellore Institute of Technology.</span></p>
                    <br>
                    <p>Ever since I was a kid, I have always been messing with computers in one way or another, 
                        which is why I took a liking to this field, and have been pursuing it ever since.
                    </p>
                    <br>
                    <p>I have a keen interest in <span class="green">web development</span> and 
                        <span class="green">software development</span> and am actively 
                        honing my skills in these fields.</p>
                    <br>
                    <p>Moreover, I am always keen on learning something new and enjoy problem solving.
                    With that said, <span class="green">experimenting and learning</span> has also always intrigued me and will always do so.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="content-img">
                    <img src="imgs/undraw_programming.svg" alt="Speaker">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="location">
                ABOUT ME
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- SKILLS SECTION  -->

        <section id="skills">
            <div class="content">
                <p>List of <span class="green">Languages, </span><span class="green">Tools </span> and <span
                        class="green">frameworks</span> that I have worked on and am fairly proficient.</p><br>
                <div class="lang-tools">
                    <div class="box">
                        <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/1/18/C_Programming_Language.svg"
                            alt="C programming" />
                        <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/1/18/ISO_C%2B%2B_Logo.svg"
                            alt="C++ programming" />
                        <img src="imgs/java.svg" alt="Java Programming">
                    </div>
                    <div class="box">
                        <img src="imgs/html.svg" alt="HTML">
                        <img src="imgs/css.svg" alt="CSS">
                        <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/99/Unofficial_JavaScript_logo_2.svg"
                            alt="javascript">
                    </div>
                    <div class="box">
                        <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/2/27/PHP-logo.svg" alt="PHP">
                        <img src="https://www.vectorlogo.zone/logos/mysql/mysql-official.svg" alt="MySQL">
                        <img src="imgs/nodejs.svg" alt="Node JS">
                        <img src="imgs/express.svg" alt="Express" id="express">
                        <img src="https://img.icons8.com/color/144/000000/mongodb.png" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="box">
                        <img src="imgs/figma.svg" alt="figma">
                        <img src="imgs/photoshop.svg" alt="photoshop">
                        <img src="imgs/vegas pro.svg" alt="Sony Vegas pro">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="location">
                SKILLS
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- PROJECTS SECTION  -->

        <section id="projects">
            <div class="content">
                <p>Few of my <span class="green">Work</span> I have done so far.
                <%- include('partials/projects') %>
            </div>
            <div class="location">
                PROJECTS
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- CONTACT SECTION  -->
        <section id="contact">
            <%if(message=='sent'){%>
                <%- include('partials/redirect') %>
            <%}%>
            <div class="content two-columns">
                <div class="content-text">
                    <form action="/sendmessage" method="post">
                        <h2>Send a message?</h2>
                        <div class="input">
                            <label for="Name">Name</label>
                            <input type="text" name="Name" id="Name" placeholder="Enter your name" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="input">
                            <label for="Email">Email ID</label>
                            <input type="email" name="Email" id="Email" placeholder="Enter your email ID" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="input">
                            <label for="Message">Message</label>
                            <textarea name="Message" id="Message" rows="8" placeholder="Enter your message"
                                required></textarea>
                        </div>
                        <button>Send message</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
                <div class="content-img">
                    <img src="imgs/vue-color-avatar2.png" alt="Speaker">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="location">
                CONTACT
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
        <script src="index.js"></script>
</body>

</html>